commit.message:
Add section "community" to contribution guide

Describe communication channels used by the Gardener project
- slack channel
- mailing list
- community documents
- meeting

Fix broken link in CONTRIBUTING.md

Fixes #17

security release process document created

we need this process description because it is required for the CNCF
badge and for participation in the Kubernetes Security Release Process
(to get predisclosures for distributors):
https://github.com/kubernetes/sig-release/blob/master/security-release-process-documentation/security-release-process.md
Adopt CNCF code of conduct for Gardener

Update documentation LICENSE to CC BY SA 4.0

Clause 11(f) of the CNCF charter says:

All documentation will be received and made available by the CNCF under the
Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License.
